data.description: Enjoy stunning architecture & gorgeous interior areas. Watch the sun rise & set from main living spaces. Truly a home that enables & enhances your lifestyle. Gourmet kitchen w/Wolf range/oven, SubZero fridge, Asko dishwasher. A second, galley kitchen w/pantry, SubZero fridge, Asko dishwasher. 3 indoor fireplaces. Patio w/outdoor fireplace, several sitting areas, spa w/outdoor shower, garden area. Unique, private home w/old growth landscaping. Minutes to State Capital, Salem Hospital, Willamette U, downtown.
